  "title": "Google 数据科学家岗位面试经验分享",
  "originalContent": "<div class=\"article_body\">\n<br/>\n整体感觉并不是很好，会有人喜欢往难了偏了问但又不觉得很有意思也不觉得很友好。但整体来说也是在预期范围之内。<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n某一轮，问了Linear regression, p value, r^2 这些概念，举了一个例子，说建了个ads model 要improve CTR，提出一堆参数来衡量这个模型的好坏，然后让你挑出其中的问题，以及怎么改进。做过模型的人应该会觉得比较简单，我一直做分析，所以模型的一些概念理解比较基本，答得一般。<br/>\n<br/>\n<div id=\"1p3a-ad-thread-paragraph\" style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px\"></div><br/>\n另一轮，说是data analysis /intuition 结果还是问了统计模型的东西。问一个linear regression里面如果training data 有重复的，dedupe 了之后有什么变了什么不变。又问了一个小题，说发了个survey 给四个选项，统计出来之后怎么确定那个选项是大家最喜欢的，是否significant。最后还问了一个小题说p-value cutoff 这个东西DS怎么决定。<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n另一轮，Write some code that would generate a new scatterplot (X,Y) dataset with 100 points. So 2 columns and 100 rows of brand new data. When you send this new dataset that you generated to me, I will fit an OLS linear regression on the data, and I want the slope to be close to 2 and the R^2 to be close to 0.8. Can you explain how you would accomplish this task? 之后又问了个case，youtube的creater 收入是来自广告的revenue，请问如果这个收入里面加上bonus会不会是个好主意。<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n另一轮，SQL<br/>\n<span style=\"display:none\"></span>Given a table (Table0) with two columns <strong>user_id</strong> and <strong>date</strong>, where a user has a row in the table for every day they were considered active on a product, find the minimum number of days that need to be considered to have over 1B unique users.<br/>\n还有个条件概率题，熟悉条件概率的话答起来不难。<br/>\n还有一个case，如果google map 加一个feature 给你推荐最佳慢跑路线，怎么衡量这个idea好不好。<br/>\n<br/>\n<div class=\"lg:w-550px bg-#fafafa p-6 mt-8 mx-auto\">\n<div class=\"flex\">\n<div class=\"w-24 text-center\">\n<a href=\"https://jobs.1point3acres.com/companies/google\" target=\"_blank\">\n<img class=\"w-full\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\"/>\n<div class=\"mt-2 text-base font-bold\">Google</div>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://jobs.1point3acres.com/companies/google/review\" target=\"_blank\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-center mt-1 space-x-1\"><img height=\"12\" src='data:image/svg+xml,&lt;svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"&gt;&lt;rect fill-opacity=\"0\"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;' style=\"background-blend-mode:normal!important;background-clip:content-box!important;background-position:50% 50%!important;background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0)!important;background-image:var(--sf-img-42)!important;background-size:100% 100%!important;background-origin:content-box!important;background-repeat:no-repeat!important\" width=\"12\"/><img height=\"12\" src='data:image/svg+xml,&lt;svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"&gt;&lt;rect fill-opacity=\"0\"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;' style=\"background-blend-mode:normal!important;background-clip:content-box!important;background-position:50% 50%!important;background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0)!important;background-image:var(--sf-img-42)!important;background-size:100% 100%!important;background-origin:content-box!important;background-repeat:no-repeat!important\" width=\"12\"/><img height=\"12\" src='data:image/svg+xml,&lt;svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"&gt;&lt;rect fill-opacity=\"0\"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;' style=\"background-blend-mode:normal!important;background-clip:content-box!important;background-position:50% 50%!important;background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0)!important;background-image:var(--sf-img-42)!important;background-size:100% 100%!important;background-origin:content-box!important;background-repeat:no-repeat!important\" width=\"12\"/><img height=\"12\" src='data:image/svg+xml,&lt;svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"&gt;&lt;rect fill-opacity=\"0\"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;' style=\"background-blend-mode:normal!important;background-clip:content-box!important;background-position:50% 50%!important;background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0)!important;background-image:var(--sf-img-42)!important;background-size:100% 100%!important;background-origin:content-box!important;background-repeat:no-repeat!important\" width=\"12\"/></div></a></div></div></div>